<p>
My Name is Haider Mirza and I am a 3D artist, Programmer and Emacs devotee.
All my projects (included this website) are cloned/hosted on <a href="https://github.com/Ha1derMirza">github</a> and are free and open-source under the GPL v3 license.
</p>
